      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "You are not building a sandcastle against the tide; you are building a fortress against the silence of your own mind. The void does not care about your feelings, but your presence is the only thing that makes the universe feel anything at all. If the universe ends in nothingness, then the only thing that truly matters is the feeling of being here right now, even if it is brief.",
